    .md-container.flex.flex-col.items-center.c-shapes.c-shapes-1.text-center
      = link_to about_partners_path, class: "c-prominent-link mt-48 mb-24" do
        = graphical_icon "arrow-left"
        See all our supporters

      %h1.text-h0.flex.flex-col.items-center.text-center
        Exercism is supported by
        %br
        = icon "packt", "Packt Publishing", category: :partners, css_class: "logo packt"

  .md-container
    %article
      .lhs
        %h2.text-h2 #{@org.name} supports Exercism
        %hr.c-divider.mt-20.mb-28
        %p.text-p-xlarge.mb-40 Packt Publishing are a core Exercism partner, helping us develop both the fundraising and content side of the platform. They have sponsored our new Fundraising role, and we are currently developing a deeper partnership which we will launch in early 2022.

